        Creates an Item Object with a temperature (double temperatureCel)
        Parameters:
        name - String variable, represents the object Name
        quantity - int variable, represents the item quantity
        cost - double variable, represents the items cost
        sellPrice - double variable, represents the items selling price
        reorderPoint - int variable, represents the items value of when to reorder
        reorderAmount - int variable, represents the items reorderamount
        temperaturecel - double variable, represents the temperature the item should be cooled at
